      <title>RecycleView实现的地区选择模块</title>
      <link>/blog/2016-09-21-recycleview%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97/</link>
